<p>After the entry class <code v-pre>SoulWebsocketClient</code> that implements Websocket communication receives the background communication, the <code v-pre>executor()</code> method called <code v-pre>WebsocketDataHandler</code> matches the information type, and calls the corresponding <code v-pre>DataHandler</code> <code v-pre>handler()</code> to process the information.</p>
